      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"balanced with respect for diversity\" sounds kinda like a way of saying it's only okay if it's not actually nationalist? like if it gets too strong it just becomes toxic. dont you think the risks of conflict and division from nationalism usually outweigh the good stuff?",
